      "content": "## ✅ Fix Complete — Summary\n\n**REVIEW-FIX.md** written to: `.planning/phases/16-session-tracker-tool-intelligence-event-tracker-deprecation-/16-REVIEW-FIX.md`\n\n### Results: 8 fixed · 2 skipped · 0 failed\n\n| Finding | Status | Commit |\n|---------|--------|--------|\n| **CR-01** subagentType heuristic | ✅ Fixed | `2473dab2` |\n| **CR-02** session-not-found envelope | ✅ Fixed | `ab1faa10` |\n| **CR-03** path-traversal guard (Windows) | ✅ Fixed | `9206e91f` |\n| **WR-01** duplicate safeSessionId | ✅ Fixed | `01bdf491` |\n| **WR-02** timeRange type mismatch | ✅ Fixed | `c2553173` |\n| **WR-03** hardcoded \"active\" status | ⏭️ Skipped (handler rewritten, no longer applicable) | — |\n| **WR-04** orphaned schema | ✅ Fixed | `7d06dc52` |\n| **WR-05** deduplication gap | ⏭️ Skipped (handler rewritten, no longer applicable) | — |\n| **IN-03** computeDepth recursion guard | ✅ Fixed | `e20732aa` |\n| **IN-04** barrel exports | ✅ Fixed | `e20732aa` |\n\n### Verification\n- `npm run typecheck` — **clean** (0 errors in modified files; 2 pre-existing errors in unrelated files)\n- `npm test` — **198 test files passed, 2424 tests passed, 0 failures**\n\n### Worktree Note\nThe temp branch `gsd-reviewfix/16-49466` was preserved because the main repo had uncommitted local changes. To merge the fixes manually:\n```bash\ngit merge --ff-only gsd-reviewfix/16-49466\ngit branch -D gsd-reviewfix/16-49466\n```",
